    from collections import deque
import sys

s = input()
n = int(input())

stkleft = deque(s)
stkright = deque()
cursor = len(stkleft)

for i in range(n):
    cmd = input().split()
    if cmd[0] == 'L':
        if stkleft:
            stkright.appendleft(stkleft.pop())
    elif cmd[0] == 'D':
        if stkright:
            stkleft.append(stkright.popleft())
    elif cmd[0] == 'B':
        if stkleft:
            stkleft.pop()
    elif cmd[0] == 'P':
        stkleft.append(cmd[1])
    print(f'{list(stkleft)}:Ïª§ÏÑú:{list(stkright)}')

print(''.join(stkleft) + ''.join(stkright))

    stkleft = list(input().strip())
stkright = []

n = int(input())

for i in range(n):
    cmd = input().split()
    if cmd[0] == 'L' and stkleft:
        stkright.append(stkleft.pop())    
    elif cmd[0] == 'D' and stkright:
            stkleft.append(stkright.pop())
    elif cmd[0] == 'B' and stkleft:
            stkleft.pop()
    elif cmd[0] == 'P':
        stkleft.append(cmd[1])
    #print(f'{stkleft}:Ïª§ÏÑú:{stkright[::-1]}')

print(''.join(stkleft+stkright[::-1]))
